column6: b'CHARDONNAY IGT TOSCANA 2018 Variety: chardonnay grapes Vinification and aging: Harvested by hand. Direct pres of whole bunches in pneumatic press. Low temperature juice racking and spontaneous fermentation. Fermentation and aging on fine lees for at least 4 months in French oak barrels. TASTING NOTES Colour: Brilliant pale straw. Notes: Enveloping, complex and refreshing nose, with notes of white flowers and vanilla. Fruitiness of peach with an elegant aroma of graphite. Palate: On the palate there is an explosion of brightness with an optimum acidity and body. The finishis full of flavor, fruity and mineral. Sustainable wine. *Must be 21 to purchase'

column6: b'Variety: Co-fermentation of Sangiovese grapes and a small amount of white grapes (Trebbiano and Vermentino). Vinification and aging: First the grapes are harvested with great care by hand. Then depending on the vintage a portion of the Rose goes through a longer maceration (2-12 hours according to the vintage); Then the grapes are soft pressed with gentle pneumatic press. The racking of the juice is always done at low temperatures and then the fermentation is spontaneous. Finally it\xe2\x80\x99s aged at least for 4 months on fine lees, then clarified and filtered. TASTING NOTES Color: Soft rose, hues of mango, and grapefruit. Notes: Crisp and refreshing on the nose, with notes of wild roses, raspberries and melon with a fading aroma of cream. Palate: Luscious, refreshing and enjoyable with well-balanced acidity. Fresh fruit on the finish. Sustainable wine. *Must be 21 to purchase'

column6: b'SANGIOVESE IGT TOSCANA Variety: Sangiovese grapes. Vinification and aging: Harvested by hand. Hand selected and de-stemmed. Spontaneous fermentation with controlled temperature in concrete and stainless steel vats. Maceration time depending on the years. Spontaneous malolactic fermentation. Aging in wood for 12 months (botti and barriques). Gentle filtered before bottling. TASTING NOTES Color: Ruby red. Notes: Intense and fragrant. Floral notes of violet and iris. Fruity notes of cherry and blackberry. Spicy notes of vanilla and pepper. Palate: Juicy, round and fresh. Good persistence. Sustainable wine. *Must be 21 to purchase'

b'Gluten Free IPA - Montreal, CA - 6% ABV - 16oz Can - Aromatic nose full of citrus, lemon and floral notes, a crisp and sharp mouthfeel paired with light caramel and hoppy flavors. A flavorful, very flavorful quencher.'

column5: b'Original Sin Black Widow Cider Can'
column6: b'Blackberry Apple Cider - New York, NY - 6% ABV - 12oz Can - The black widow is fruit-forward, yet tart, with a tantalizing complexity, made with blackberries and freshly pressed New York apples.'

column5: b'Peak Organic Fresh Cut Pilsner Can'
column6: b'Bohemian Pilsner - Portland, ME - 4.6% ABV - 12oz Can - Fresh Cut is a dry-hopped pilsner. Chinook, Citra and Centennial hops provide aromas of citrus, grass and spice. Though the front palate is loud with IPA qualities, the finish is distinctly pilsner- crisp, dry and extremely refreshing.'

b"Double IPA - Brooklyn, NY - 9.1% ABV - 12oz Can - We remember our first sip of hoppy beer, do you? Nearly spit that $#!^ out. Now we fantasize about this stuff. Thinking about those hop ones...bursting with juice...ripe as all hell...makes you look forward to that first RESIN\xc2\xae all day long. Can't wait."
b'Passion Fruit, Mango, Pineapple, Watermelon Kiwi - 5% ABV - 12oz Can - Made with simple ingredients and hints of our favorite fruits. Never made with artificial sweeteners or flavors.'

b'Sonoma, CA - 2017 - 14.5% ABV - 750 ML - Deep, rich, and concentrated in color and texture with ripe strawberry, red cherry, and wild berry fruit. Hints of spice and cola with firm tannins in the finish.'

b'Colchagua Valley, Chile - 2014 - 14% ABV - 750ML - Aromas of plastic, pencil eraser and tire rubber sit atop herbal berry and plum scents. On the palate, this Cabernet-led blend feels choppy, bumpy and grating. Herbal plum, tobacco, oak and chocolate flavors finish fresh and snappy, with a lasting green note.'

b'Veneto, Italy - 2019 - 11% ABV - 750ML - Tiamo Prosecco has a green straw color and charming aromas of apples and pears and gardenia flowers. On the palate is it bright, fresh and fruity with fine bubbles.'

b'Monteray, CA - 2019 - 14.1% ABV - 750ML - A golden yellow shade hints at the rich scents and flavors swirling in the glass. Tropical aromas of pineapple, guava and white peach are lifted by notes of pickled ginger and plumeria. The exotic nose translates to a similar flavor profile featuring mango, passion fruit and orange zest.'

b'Fuel your day with every last bite of chicken and bacon you\xe2\x80\x99d get in your go-to Footlong, now in a bowl. Add veggies and ranch to the mix and it all adds up to a power packed Chicken & Bacon Ranch Protein Bowl.'

b'Can\xe2\x80\x99t pick just one protein for your Protein Bowl? Try three. The Cold Cut Combo features heaping portions of ham, salami and bologna (all turkey based) plus lettuce, tomato, cucumbers and more.'

b'Big. Meaty. Tasty. And we mean meaty. You\xe2\x80\x99ll get all the salami, pepperoni and ham you\xe2\x80\x99d find on a Footlong Italian B.M.T\xc2\xae. on top of shredded lettuce, tomatoes, cucumbers and more. Yeah, that works.'

b'When it comes to the Meatball Marinara Protein Bowl, we won\xe2\x80\x99t skimp on the protein. You\xe2\x80\x99ll get spinach, peppers and other veggies plus all eight meatballs (count \xe2\x80\x98em!) you\xe2\x80\x99d find on a Footlong.'

b'Our Protein Bowls got their name for a reason. Because they\xe2\x80\x99re stacked with the meats you love. Oven Roasted Chicken is no exception. Loaded with veggies and topped with all the savory chicken you\xe2\x80\x99d get on a Footlong \xe2\x80\x94 this one\xe2\x80\x99s a power meal.'

b'How do you turn your go-to Spicy Italian into a powerful Protein Bowl? You take all of the pepperoni and Genoa salami (seriously, every last slice!) you\xe2\x80\x99d find on a Footlong and add it to a bowl with your pick of veggies.'

b'Packed with protein and stacked with veggies, the Steak & Cheese Protein Bowl is everything you love about your favorite Footlong \xe2\x80\x94 literally, it has the same amount of juicy steak \xe2\x80\x94 plus peppers, onions and more.'

b'Pile up the protein with a Sweet Onion Chicken Teriyaki Protein Bowl. And we really mean pile. It\xe2\x80\x99s an entire Footlong\xe2\x80\x99s worth of teriyaki-glazed chicken plus veggies drizzled with sweet onion sauce.'

Wrap it up in a tomato basil wrap with lettuce, spinach, tomatoes, cucumbers, green peppers, and red onions. Get ready for a big bite of awesome.'
